---
title: "Funding"
layout: "layouts/subpage.njk"
permalink: /funding/index.html
---
{% set fundedProjects = collections
    .fundedProjects[0]
    .data
    .fundedProjects %}

<div class="stack-m">
    <div class="wrapper | stack-xl" style="--wrapper-max: var(--wrapper-m);">
        <div class="stack-s">
            <h1 class="uppercase font-head text-purple weight-bold text-step-4">We fund open ideas</h1>

            <div class="text-side-by-side sidebar-right" style="
                --sidebar-width: clamp(22rem, 30vw, 30rem);
                --sidebar-gap: var(--space-l);
                --sidebar-threshold: 40rem;
                ">
                <div class="stack-m">
                    <p class="text-step-1">Are you working on an open source firmware project and need financial support to move it forward?</p>
                    <p class="text-step-1"> We believe in empowering developers, researchers, and communities building the future of trustworthy technology. That’s why we offer direct support to help your project grow.</p>
                </div>
                <aside class="stack-xs">
                    <p class="text-step-0 text-gray-dark">Curious what kind of projects we're supporting?</p>
                    <a href="/projects/" class="link text-step--1">View Projects</a>
                </aside>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="stack-m">
            <h3 class="text-center uppercase text-step-3 text-purple font-head">Open Calls</h3>
            {% set hasOpenCalls = false %}
            {% for funding in collections.funding %}
                {% if funding.data.status != 'closed' %}
                    {% set hasOpenCalls = true %}
                {% endif %}
            {% endfor %}

            {% if hasOpenCalls %}
            <ul role="list" class="stack-m">
                {% for funding in collections.funding %}
                    {% if funding.data.status != 'closed' %}
                    <li class="edge-card">
                        <div class="sidebar-right" style="
                            --sidebar-threshold: 30rem;
                            --sidebar-gap: var(--space-l);
                            --sidebar-gap-vertical: var(--space-m);
                        ">
                            <div>
                                <div class="edge-card__header">
                                    <h3 class="uppercase text-step-2 font-head weight-bold">{{funding.data.title}}</h3>
                                </div>
                                <div class="edge-card__content">
                                    <p class="weight-medium text-step--1">{{funding.data.subtitle}}</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="stack-m">
                                <div class="stack-xxs">
                                    <h4 class="uppercase font-head text-step--1 weight-bold">Status</h4>
                                    <div class="text-purple text-step-0" style="display: flex; gap: var(--space-xxs);">
                                        <span class="border-label" style="width: 5rem">Open</span>{{ funding.data.open }}
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="text-purple text-step-0" style="display: flex; gap: var(--space-xxs);">
                                        <span class="border-label" style="width: 5rem">Closes</span>{{ funding.data.closes }}
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="stack-xxs">
                                    <h4 class="uppercase font-head text-step--1 weight-bold">Category / Focus</h4>
                                    <p class="weight-medium text-step--1">{{ funding.data.categories | join(' · ') }}</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="edge-card__footer">
                            <a href="/funding/{{ funding.data.title | slugify }}/" class="btn btn--small">More Info & Application</a>
                            {% icon icon = "osff-sign",
                            alt = "OSFF",
                            class = "edge-card__footer-icon",
                            width = "var(--space-m)" %}
                        </div>
                    </li>
                    {% endif %}
                {% endfor %}
            </ul>
            {% else %}
            <div class="info-box | stack-s" style="max-width: 50rem; margin: 0 auto;">
                <p class="text-step-0">There are currently no open funding calls. However, we're always interested in supporting impactful open source firmware projects.</p>
                <p class="text-step-0">If you have a proposal, please reach out to us at <a href="mailto:cfp+open@osfw.foundation" class="link">cfp+open@osfw.foundation</a> and we'll be happy to discuss your project.</p>
            </div>
            {% endif %}
        </div>

        <div class="stack-m">
            <h3 class="text-center uppercase text-step-3 text-purple font-head">Closed Calls</h3>
            <ul role="list" class="stack-m">
                {% for funding in collections.funding %}
                    {% if funding.data.status == 'closed' %}
                    <li class="edge-card">
                        <div class="sidebar-right" style="
                            --sidebar-threshold: 30rem;
                            --sidebar-gap: var(--space-l);
                            --sidebar-gap-vertical: var(--space-m);
                        ">
                            <div>
                                <div class="edge-card__header">
                                    <h3 class="uppercase text-step-2 font-head weight-bold">{{funding.data.title}}</h3>
                                </div>
                                <div class="edge-card__content">
                                    <p class="weight-medium text-step--1">{{funding.data.subtitle}}</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="stack-m">
                                <div class="stack-xxs">
                                    <h4 class="uppercase font-head text-step--1 weight-bold">Status</h4>
                                    <div class="text-gray-dark text-step-0" style="display: flex; gap: var(--space-xxs);">
                                        <span class="border-label" style="width: 5rem">Opened</span>{{ funding.data.open }}
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="text-gray-dark text-step-0" style="display: flex; gap: var(--space-xxs);">
                                        <span class="border-label" style="width: 5rem">Closed</span>{{ funding.data.closes }}
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="stack-xxs">
                                    <h4 class="uppercase font-head text-step--1 weight-bold">Category / Focus</h4>
                                    <p class="weight-medium text-step--1">{{ funding.data.categories | join(' · ') }}</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="edge-card__footer">
                            <a href="/funding/{{ funding.data.title | slugify }}/" class="btn btn--small">View Details</a>
                            {% icon icon = "osff-sign",
                            alt = "OSFF",
                            class = "edge-card__footer-icon",
                            width = "var(--space-m)" %}
                        </div>
                    </li>
                    {% endif %}
                {% endfor %}
            </ul>
        </div>

        {% if fundedProjects and fundedProjects.length > 0 %}
        <div class="stack-m">
            <h3 class="uppercase text-step-2 text-purple font-head">Funded Projects</h3>
            <p class="text-step-0">Projects that have received funding from the Open Source Firmware Foundation.</p>

            <ul role="list" class="grid-switcher" style="
                --gs-columns-medium: 1;
                --gs-columns-large: 2;
                --gs-gap: var(--space-m);
            ">
                {% for project in fundedProjects %}
                    <li class="edge-card">
                        <div class="edge-card__header">
                            {% if project.logo %}
                                {% if project.logo.includes(".png") or project.logo.includes(".jpg") or project.logo.includes(".svg") %}
                                    <img src="{{ project.logo }}" alt="{{ project.title }}" class="edge-card__header-icon">
                                {% else %}
                                    {% icon icon = project.logo,
                                  alt = project.title,
                                  class = "edge-card__header-icon"
                                  %}
                                {% endif %}
                            {% endif %}
                            <h3 class="uppercase text-step-2 font-head weight-bold">{{ project.title }}</h3>
                        </div>

                        <div class="edge-card__content">
                            <p class="weight-medium text-step--1">{{ project.description }}</p>
                            <div class="stack-xxs" style="margin-top: var(--space-s);">
                                {% if project.project %}
                                <p class="text-step--1"><strong>Project:</strong> {{ project.project }}</p>
                                {% endif %}
                                {% if project.fundingRound %}
                                <p class="text-step--1"><strong>Funding Round:</strong> <a href="/funding/{{ project.fundingRound | slugify }}/" class="link">{{ project.fundingRound }}</a></p>
                                {% endif %}
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="edge-card__footer">
                            {% if project.url %}
                            <a href="{{ project.url }}" class="btn btn--small" target="_blank">More info</a>
                            {% endif %}
                            {% icon icon = "osff-sign",
                      alt = "OSFF",
                      class = "edge-card__footer-icon",
                      width = "var(--space-l)" %}
                        </div>
                    </li>
                {% endfor %}
            </ul>
        </div>
        {% endif %}
    </div>
</div>

<div class="text-white funding-teaser bg-purple">
    <div class="wrapper | stack-l">
        <div class="stack-m">
            <h2 class="text-center uppercase font-head text-salmon weight-bold text-step-4">Funding Without the Fuss</h2>
            <p class="text-center text-step-1">We keep it simple: if you're working on something that aligns with our mission — open, trustworthy, and accessible firmware — let’s talk.</p>
            <p class="text-center text-step-1">We support early-stage ideas, ongoing projects, and everything in between. Whether you're a solo developer, a team, or part of an organization, we want to hear from you.</p>
        </div>
        <hr>
        <div class="stack-m">
            <h3 class="text-step-3 font-head">Here's how it works:</h3>
            <ul class="fancy-list fancy-list--light | text-step-0" role="list">
                <li>Send us a short proposal: Tell us what you're building, why it matters, and what kind of support you need.</li>
                <li>We'll review it quickly: Our team will get back to you and might ask for more details.</li>
                <li>Get funded: If there's a fit, we’ll support you—financially and beyond.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white funding-teaser__cta stack-xs">
            <p class="text-step-0 text-gray-dark">Curious if your idea fits?<br> Don’t hesitate to reach out.</p>
            <a href="/projects/" class="link text-step--1">View Projects</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>